metadata.name: Rug World #1
metadata.description: In the vast expanse of the crypto universe, there exist planets unlike anything ever seen before. These animated planets are covered in rugs of all colors and patterns, each one imbued with a unique personality and charm. As they rotate through space, the rugs ripple and sway, creating a mesmerizing dance that draws in all who gaze upon them. These planets are home to a variety of digital beings, from mischievous meme creatures to wise cosmic elders. And as they journey through the cryptospaces, they discover new worlds, form alliances, and build communities that are as diverse and colorful as the rugs that cover their surfaces.
